# List of OpenAccess reference libraries. The first library in the list 
	# indicates the library that will be used for technology information unless 
	# init_oa_design_lib or init_oa_tech_lib are specified. All cells from 
	# the specified libraries are read. It is important to include the standard 
	# cell library in the list to make sure that cells that are not in the 
	# current netlist are read and available for optimization. The init_abstract_view 
	# and init_layout_view lists specify which views of the cells are read. 
	# Used by the init_design command.